This paper deals with the wiretap channel, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT) and cryptography (cs.CR). It also discusses channel uncertainty and malicious interference, which are relevant to signal processing (cs.SI) and multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper involves communication networks (cs.NI) as it considers the transmission of messages between two users.
